  m_sTitle "B. Friendly Forces:"
  m_sTextData "Disposition:"\
  "Company is located to the SE securing our far right flank with our other platoons while our recon forces were recently pushed back into Pustoshka."\
  ""\
  "Higher Units Mission:"\
  "Battalion has been assigned to support the local CDF in their defence and recapture of territory from the USSR forces and providing aid to the civilians."\
  ""\
  "Composition:"\
  "1x Mechanized Platoon (++)"\
  ""\
  "Strength:"\
  "Mechanized Platoon (++) at 62x man strength"\
  "4x M113A2s"\
  "2x LAVIIs"\
  "2x M252 Mortars"\
  ""\
  "Supporting Fires:"\
  "M252 Mortar support available"\
  ""\
  "Attachments/Detachments:"\
  "1x Mortar Attachment"\
  "2x Mechanized LAV Squad Attachments"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 {
  coords 3006.573 303.124 7986.115
  m_sTitle "II. Mission:"
  m_sTextData "Our strengthened platoon is tasked with securing the town of Vybor by taking over the COY HQ building in the town, and the factory office building in the factory district, while fighting off any remnant forces of the recons in the area or sweeping the area clear of them."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 {
  coords 3006.85 303.114 7986.082
  m_sTitle "III. Execution:"
  m_sTextData "Intent:"\
  "Platoon is to decide on the attack direction, sweep it of potential recon elements and assault the town of Vybor and the factory district."\
  ""\
  "1. Concept of the Operation:"\
  "Platoon Commander's Discretion."\
  "It is advised to not allow the enemy to ambush our LAVs and M113A2s while the infantry are still mounted, push the infantry to screen and sweep the forest. "\
  ""\
  "Utilize the Mortars to clear our dug in enemy positions or to flush out enemies from a forest if required, worst case use mortars to demolished fortified buildings."\
  ""\
  "2. Maneuver"\
  "Platoon Commander's Discretion."\
  "It is advised to not spread our forces too wide where upon our units cannot support one another incase of attack, ambush or being seperated."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_CAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
